{"tid":2050424,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"新 iOS 版本確認 Apple 正研擬販售服務組合包","createTime":"2020-06-04T06:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T03:29:38.000Z","uid":4646,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"75486c6a27c07a44334638a2248563c1d7bf83e4","tid":2050424,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T06:26:09.000Z","msg":"先前曾有傳言指出 Apple 將會為旗下服務單一組合包，以更優惠的價格吸引用戶，試圖增加其它服務的客戶群。而今日根據外媒 9to5Mac 報導，他們在 iOS 13.5.5 Beta 的程式碼中，就發現了該組合服務實際上正在開發當中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Apple-Music-1536x804.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2FApple-Music-1536x804.jpg&h=c11c42af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據悉，iOS 13.5.5 的內部文件包含了「Bundle Offer」以及「Bundle Subscription」等描述，而這些並不在先前的 iOS 版本當中，此外這些程式碼也指向 Apple 自家數位服務的管理系統，因此外媒相信該組合包也是為 Apple 數位服務所推出。<br />\n<br />\n而這可能意味著先前傳言的 Apple 服務組合包是確有其事，因此往後你可能只需要支付單一費用，就能夠享用 Apple Music、Apple TV+ 及其他 Apple 相關服務。"},{"pid":"c3f76f5abbbfe17622afd633711fc6f25e2b76ef","tid":2050424,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T06:28:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/06/04/apple-bundle-service-in-ios-13-5-5-beta-code/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F06%2F04%2Fapple-bundle-service-in-ios-13-5-5-beta-code%2F&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY6hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=f9eeefd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/06/04/apple-bundle-service-in-ios-13-5-5-beta-code/</a>"},{"pid":"b93f88474a8bdf1af7deb93925aee24738458ba8","tid":2050424,"uid":185652,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T06:30:35.000Z","msg":"Apple霸權，apple高牆"},{"pid":"aef93002e95a54234e09d06e246e26fb26085274","tid":2050424,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T06:34:20.000Z","msg":